Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:38.10,Default - Top,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Odokawa-sama, I'm delighted to see \Nthat you're doing well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:39.35,Default - Top,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't call me that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.35,0:23:41.19,Default - Top,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you believe in fate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:44.17,Default - Top,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's fate that brought us together again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:46.88,Default - Top,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I pick up repeat passengers \Nin that area all the time while cruising.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:47.82,Default - Top,IMAI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But one billion—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:49.94,Default - Top,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shh! Keep your voice down.{\i0}